I"ƒ<p>Described in a new Methods in Ecology and Evolution paper <a href="http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.2041-210X.2011.00180.x/abstract">here</a>, a new <a href="http://cran.r-project.org/">R</a> package <a href="http://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/RNetLogo/index.html">RNetLogo</a> allows you to use <a href="http://ccl.northwestern.edu/netlogo/">NetLogo</a> from R.</p>

